lead_paragraph: Gary Payton II had 22 points, 15 rebounds, eight assists and four steals, leading Oregon State over No. 21 Southern California 85-70 Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Payton II Leads Oregon State Over No. 21 USC 85-70
